function Start()

	idMotherClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(idMother)
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idMotherClone) then
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idMotherClone, idMotherLoc, "NPC_Walk_Fast", true)
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idMotherClone, idMotherLoc)
		Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(idMotherClone)
	end
	
	idOctaviaClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(idOctavia)
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idOctaviaClone) then
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idOctaviaClone, idOctaviaLoc, "NPC_Walk_Fast", true)
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idOctaviaClone, idOctaviaLoc)
	end
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idMotherClone) and Hydra.ActorIsValid(idOctaviaClone) then
		Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(idMotherClone)
		Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(convCellarDoor, idSelf, idOctaviaClone, idMotherHouse)
	end
	
end

function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)

	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idOctaviaClone) then
		Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(idOctaviaClone, convCellarDoor)
		Hydra.QActorDeleteNPCClone(idOctaviaClone, 0.5)
	end
	
end
